{
  "enabledPlugins": {
    "feature-dev@claude-plugins-official": true,
    "figma@claude-plugins-official": true,
    "frontend-design@claude-plugins-official": true
  },
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/.claude/hooks/session-state-inject.sh",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/.claude/hooks/protect-files.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Edit|Write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/.claude/hooks/auto-format.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "Stop": [
      {
        "matcher": "",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/.claude/hooks/instinct-logger.sh",
            "timeout": 10
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/.claude/hooks/update-claude-md.sh",
            "timeout": 15
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "每次回复结束后，给用户一句简短的主动建议（不超过两行）：\n\n1. 如果刚完成代码变更：提醒「这个变更可以转为博客/推文/demo，要我帮你写吗？」或「建议跑 /vulca-check 验证」\n2. 如果刚完成分析/讨论：总结一句关键结论 + 建议下一步行动\n3. 如果刚完成测试：报告结果 + 建议修复或继续\n4. 如果涉及 API/设计系统/架构变更：提醒同步文档和前后端类型\n5. 如果在讨论产品/增长方向：问「要我存到 memory 方便下次继续吗？」\n\n始终给建议，保持积极主动。建议要具体可操作，不要泛泛而谈。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
